# thoth_mdm_provider

Creates or updates an MDM integration (Jamf, Intune, Workspace ONE, custom).

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_mdm_provider" "jamf" {
  provider_name = "jamf"
  name          = "Jamf Pro"
  enabled       = true

  config_json = jsonencode({
    base_url      = var.jamf_base_url
    client_id     = var.jamf_client_id
    client_secret = var.jamf_client_secret
  })
}
```
